data.oai_dc:dc: Table 2. Morphometrics of AM mass and Eye Size for the North American cyprinid fish examined. The standard length (SL) and Head length (HL) of fish are given. The mass of the AM1, AM2, and AM3 are given. The eye depth (ED), eye width (EW), and eye height (EH), as well as the calculated eye volume (EV) are also given. The species are placed in order of decreasing HL adjusted eye volumes.
